.TH "simtec_hw_params" 9 "simtec_hw_params" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
simtec_hw_params \- update hardware parameters
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" simtec_hw_params
.BI "(struct snd_pcm_substream *substream "  ","
.BI "struct snd_pcm_hw_params *params "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "substream" 12
The audio substream instance.
.IP "params" 12
The parameters requested.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Update the codec data routing and configuration  settings
from the supplied data.
